ing his paper and - and - well - your evening had gone then hadn't it. And of course he had his garden, well, he used to go into the garden and - and then it was the weekend.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7626777 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid476072\charrsid10379359 Did he ever attend the races or out a bet on?
