 nearly all from being young you see because - there weren't many but what went to the church and we knew them from being little but of course that didn't make any difference. It - we had to do as we was told.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7626777 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid476072\charrsid10379359 Were they particular about things like manners and tidiness?
