chers and - and - there was the headmaster and there was two men teachers and they was in the fifth and sixth form. All the others was - ladies you see. You must had them in when the boys were getting bigger. They - they had 'em. Oh yes, they used to stra
ighten 'em up. Mind you they needed it.
