Well - well I don't think they really said much because they - they - they knew I wanted to go}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid874559\charrsid10379359  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid476072\charrsid10379359 and - and - I expect they thought, well, if she wants to go - and I - I was right happy. But - I only stayed there - 'til I was thirteen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7626777 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid476072\charrsid10379359 What exactly did you have to do?
