Well - one week it'd be a bit longer than the other. We went at six o'clock in the morning. And then we had a break for breakfast. Half an hour I think. And then half past twelve I think. And then we had to have our dinner and I h
ad to get washed and changed to go to school then. And then - it - the other week - yes, and - went in the afternoon to work.
