No, well you see - there weren't no voting for such as us you know. I never voted 'til I got }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4348380 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
