\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7626777 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid476072\charrsid10379359 The Keighley Cons?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11083444 HO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid476072\charrsid10379359 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7626777 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid476072\charrsid10379359 What's that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11083444 HO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid476072\charrsid10379359 
Conversas you know the - the - it was a - it was a - the mechanics in Keighley and it - it - there was dancing and all different things and all the nobility of Keighley went to first night Monday night and 
- I think it was about a guinea. Well they used to all have their - the - the carriages come and - remember going up every night up to Keighley to watch them come in you know and - beautiful dresses and - oh yes, oh it was a - a wonderful affair was that.
 Oh - and I went when - I were right young. We used to have a Christmas concert at the church and I can remember twice being a fairy and - all tinsel on me silk dress and I went to the Cons in it. Yes. I thought it were wonderful. Things like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7626777 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid476072\charrsid10379359 Did you make any new friends about this time after you left school?
