e are and I got to know Roland through - through her. She invited - I used to go up there to tea you know and she used to come to our house to tea and - oh yes, I made a lot of friends at work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7626777 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid476072\charrsid10379359 About how old would you be when you started courting then?
