And - and then these friends - I had a friend that lived just by - well, we used to meet these other friends, they didn't live by us but we had a certain place where we met and then on a Wednesday we always went to the pictures. And other nights well we -
 we went for walks and things like that. Perhaps call - dark weather we'd call at the fish and chip shop. We didn't in summer though.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7626777 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid476072\charrsid10379359 Did you have to be in by a certain time?
